User segmentation is important on the basis of 
1. user activity - passive followers can usually use pull notification model
2. time of the day 
3. is there any special occassion
4. what is the time zone

// push architecture have a high load for a small time whereas latency is low 
// pull architecture have gradual load increase till peak of the day and then it decreases
// batched push notification is how you balance 
// between push and pull , you can have a message queue for pace handling , the consumers of the message queue